    &lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insert Table&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;p class=&quot;key-points&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; alt=&quot;Key Points&quot;&gt;
        &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insert Table&lt;/strong&gt; is a feature in Microsoft Word that allows users to create a table by specifying the number of rows and columns.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;When you select &quot;Insert Table,&quot; a dialog box appears where you can define the table&#039;s dimensions.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;It is a quick and easy way to create tables without manually drawing them.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;You can later customize the table by adding or removing rows and columns, merging cells, and applying different styles.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;This feature is commonly used in documents for organizing data into a structured format.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;

    &lt;p class=&quot;additional-information&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; alt=&quot;Additional Information&quot;&gt;
        &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;In addition to &quot;Insert Table,&quot; Microsoft Word offers other table-related features such as &quot;Draw Table,&quot; &quot;Quick Tables,&quot; and various &quot;Table Styles&quot; for further customization.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;&quot;Draw Table&quot; allows users to manually draw the table&#039;s cells, which can be useful for creating complex table layouts.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;&quot;Quick Tables&quot; provide pre-designed table templates that can be inserted and customized as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Using tables in Word documents improves readability and helps present information clearly and professionally.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;

